@startuml sequence_tenant_filter_bootstrap
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Tenant Query Filter Hardening - Sequence

participant "HTTP Request" as Req
participant "TenantContextMiddleware" as TCM
participant "FleetHubDbContext" as Db
participant "Feature Handler" as H
database "SQL Server" as SQL

Req -> TCM : authenticated request
TCM -> TCM : resolve active organization
TCM -> Db : set scoped tenant state

Req -> H : business operation
H -> Db : query Equipment / WorkOrders
Db -> Db : apply HasQueryFilter\nTenantResolved && OrgId match
Db -> SQL : filtered query
SQL --> Db : tenant rows only
Db --> H : filtered results

== Bootstrap path ==

TCM -> Db : IgnoreQueryFilters()\nfor user / membership lookup
Db -> SQL : explicit unfiltered query

@enduml
